videos.description: Virginia's Jack Salt starts the game off with a two-handed slam giving Virginia an early lead.
videos.headline: Virginia opens game with dunk from Salt

videos.description: Duke's Marques Bolden rejects Virginia's Marial Shayok on his drive to the basket.
videos.headline: Marques Bolden protects the rim for Duke

videos.description: Virginia's Marial Shayok makes a late layup on a second chance opportunity to cap off a 7-0 Virginia run at the end of the half.
videos.headline: Virginia ends half on 7-0 run with Shayok layup

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum hits three straight shots to go on a 7-0 run for Duke.
videos.headline: Jayson Tatum scores seven straight points for Duke

videos.description: Duke's Luke Kennard makes a jumper after appearing to be bloodied during the game.
videos.headline: Being bloodied can't stop Kennard from hitting a jumper

videos.description: Duke's Jayson Tatum makes 3-pointers on back-to-back possessions to give Duke a 54-44 lead.
videos.headline: Tatum knocks down back-to-back 3-pointers to expand Duke lead

videos.description: Breaking down Jayson Tatum's performance in Duke's 65-55 win against Virginia.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Duke's 65-55 victory over Virginia
